_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:4:"text";s:162:"im excited for a group, thematic thing. ive enver really felt part of a group. you could say im... looking for group? ah hah... hah hah hah... hah.. *ba-dum tish*";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914092";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13859140925";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:124919;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"124919";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:4:"text";s:474:"but, if that&#039;s the case, then go ahead and peek into BMs profile, save a copy of the blue sparkly crystal gif, and use that as your cutie mark. water fits red mage best, seeing as traditionally the element of water in magic, aside from physical water, is associated with versatility and adaptability, as well as trade and commerce. it can be gentle, flowing and flexible, or it can be harsh and brutal, but it is not the best at any of these things. just like red mage.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914192";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13859141921";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:124921;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"124921";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:4:"text";s:188:"... of course, this means i should get to work on additional sprites, because i wanted to involve little pixel animations much more heavily in the profiles than just the teeny sparklies...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914247";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13859142470";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:124923;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"124923";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"20";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"327";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:70:"Done and done. And I like the teeny sparklies. They&#039;re tasteful. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914339";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fe2c2c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13859143381";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#fa072f";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:124925;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"124925";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:4:"text";s:629:"well, i wanted to make larger versions (not too large, but still bigger) of each crystal color, so each profile would ahve one crystal color in it bigger than the others. black mage would ahve a bigger than usual fire crystal, because thats the crystal he holds. yours would ahve a bigger than average water crystal, etcetera. i also wanted to make more -generic- sparklies, just the sparks of magic, in each color for characters or instances where one is associated with an element, but doesn&#039;t hold a crystal for it. as unlikely as it is for our group to get that big, like.. almost impossible, i stil lwanna cover it. ^_^";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914503";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13859145031";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:124926;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"124926";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"20";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Red_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"327";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:65:"I don&#039;t know. A lot of ponies might want to get in on this. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1385914581";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fe2c2c